6'),('5aaa70a5ce4a27f867527147','<div class=\"markdown-text\"><p>回复</p>\n</div>','592f8ef01e7e75f60c1ad80d','UyoVCEta4hUrCfoQfx8MFoVy',NULL,'2018-03-15 13:09:57'),('5aaa9805f5dfc27d7ad98856','<div class=\"markdown-text\"><p><a href=\"/user/445141126\">@445141126</a> 如果有活跃的<code>request</code>突然进来就可以跳出阻塞。例如http服务器会一直阻塞<code>poll</code>阶段，直到有请求进来</p>\n</div>','5a9108d78d6e16e56bb80882','565553143325bb2c4ebd803a','5aaa3dc719b2e3db18959df2','2018-03-15 15:57:57'),('5aab0fd419b2e3db18959e25','<div class=\"markdown-text\"><p>deps/uv/src/unix/core.c</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\"><code>int uv_backend_timeout(const uv_loop_t* loop) {\n  if (loop-&gt;stop_flag != 0)\n    return 0;\n\n  if (!uv__has_active_handles(loop) &amp;&amp; !uv__has_active_reqs(loop))\n    return 0;\n\n  if (!QUEUE_EMPTY(&amp;loop-&gt;idle_handles))\n    return 0;\n\n  if (loop-&gt;closing_handles)\n    return 0;\n\n  return uv__next_timeout(loop);\n}\n</code></pre><p>deps/uv/src/unix/timer.c</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\"><code>int uv__next_timeout(const uv_loop_t* loop) {\n  const struct heap_node* heap_node;\n  const uv_timer_t* handle;\n  uint64_t diff;\n\n  heap_node = heap_min((const struct heap*) &amp;loop-&gt;timer_heap);\n  if (heap_node == NULL)\n    return -1; &#x2F;* block indefinitely *&#x2F; \n\n  handle = container_of(heap_node, const uv_timer_t, heap_node);\n  if (handle-&gt;timeout &lt;= loop-&gt;time)\n    return 0;\n\n  diff = handle-&gt;timeout - loop-&gt;time;\n  if (diff &gt; INT_MAX)\n    diff = INT_MAX;\n\n  return diff;\n}\n</code></pre><p>再读一遍明白了设计意图了，有任务就赶紧干，没任务就等，不让CPU空转。</p>\n</div>','5a9108d78d6e16e56bb80882','nrEFV7ag6aMDeraJHd4Cxjqv',NULL,'2018-03-16 00:29:08'),('5aac8c67ce4a27f8675271c4','<div class=\"markdown-text\"><p>123123</p>\n</div>','592f8ef01e7e75f60c1ad80d','VdCYS6egi9iVStkkpaSC497g',NULL,'2018-03-17 03:32:56'),('5aac8c79e7b166bb7b9ecb28','<div class=\"markdown-text\"><p><a href=\"/user/feshy2013\">@feshy2013</a> test</p>\n</div>','592f8ef01e7e75f60c1ad80d','